London Page 2 Photograph Nato's secretary-general, Mr Manfred Worner (left),
pictured at a meeting in Moscow yesterday with President Boris Yeltsin.
Speaking after two days of talks with Russian leaders, he hailed a new era
of trust and co-operation with the Commonwealth of Independent States and
said they would work together to stop the spread of nuclear weapons.
(Omitted).
