<HEADLINE>
FT  26 FEB 92 / World News in Brief: N Korea 'almost nuclear'
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
CIA director Robert Gates said North Korea could have a nuclear weapon
within a few months.
</TEXT>
<PUB>The Financial Times
</PUB>
<PAGE>
London Page 1
