dollar facility of Dollars 33.5m (Pounds 19.1m), reducing to Dollars 23m on
July 1 and to Dollars 20m on October 1.
Mr Stuart Macdonald, finance director, said his goal was to reduce gearing,
currently well over 200 per cent, to under 100 per cent by the year end.
