<TEXT>
The Merseyside fraud squad is investigating Alan Paul, the hairdressing and
beauty company placed in receivership last December.
Papers are being evaluated by the Crown Prosecution Service, but police have
refused to discuss details of the investigation. Questions were raised ahead
